trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLinesCollection> class represents a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine> objects, and is implemented as the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.StripLines%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> class.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLinesCollection> classe rappresenta una raccolta di <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine> oggetti e viene implementato come il <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.StripLines%2A> proprietà del <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> classe.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine> objects can be appended, inserted or removed from the collection at both design time and run time.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine> gli oggetti possono essere aggiunti, inseriti o rimosso dall'insieme in fase di progettazione e fase di esecuzione.

trans-unit.source: **Note** Strip lines can be displayed once or repeatedly for a set interval.
trans-unit.target: **Nota** strisce possono essere visualizzate una o più volte per un intervallo specificato.
